            <title>[CASSANDRA-16942] Remove OrderedJUnit4ClassRunner</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-16942</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Tests in a class should not depend on the order they are run in, remove &lt;tt&gt;OrderedJUnit4ClassRunner&lt;/tt&gt; and fix any tests that depend on it&lt;/p&gt;</description>
